    template.print('<p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>üìé Authority Limits Comparison</strong></p>');
    template.print('<p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">A detailed comparison of authority limits has been attached to this email as a PDF for your review.</p>');
    template.print('</div>');

    // Then continue with your existing mail script logic...
    var documentRecord, parent;
    
    // ... rest of your existing code
Step 4: Test

Create a test signature authority request
Submit it for approval
Check that:

PDF is generated and attached to the parent record
Approval notification is sent
PDF is attached to the email
Email body references the PDF
